        {
            "title": "水警港島薄扶林反走私  檢832萬元懷疑私煙",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方檢獲183箱懷疑私煙。警方提供\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3a07df494e1a12590c3b68104cf9f32e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040414184882960.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方檢獲183箱懷疑私煙。警方提供</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>水警總區特遣隊、水警南分區聯同海關海域聯合特遣隊人員經過深入調查及情報分析後，懷疑近日有不法份子在薄扶林一帶進行走私活動。人員今日（4日）凌晨在薄扶林一帶進行反走私行動。\n\n</p>\n<p>行動中，人員發現一艘沒有亮起航行燈的可疑快艇駛至沙灣道對開岸邊，同時有數名可疑男子將貨物由快艇搬至岸上一輛貨車上。人員隨即採取行動，該批男子跳上快艇後高速往南面水域方向逃去。水警人員遂展開追截，惟快艇最終逃離香港南面水域往內地方向駛去。\n\n</p>\n<p>人員在該輛貨車上及岸邊共檢獲183箱懷疑私煙，估計總市值共約832萬元，應課稅值約604萬元。人員亦扣查有關涉案貨車，案件由相關部門繼續跟進調查。\n\n</p>\n<p>買賣私煙屬違法行為。根據《應課稅品條例》，任何人若處理、管有、售賣或購買私煙即屬違法，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款100萬元及監禁兩年。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062105/即時-港聞-水警港島薄扶林反走私-檢832萬元懷疑私煙",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-04 14:26:02",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "筲箕灣東大街住宅地估值逾5億 業界：規模細具吸引力",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"筲箕灣東大街住宅地估值逾5億 業界：規模細具吸引力\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a99f21f4d04a36cb63f3fac55a0ad406/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040414172239576.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">筲箕灣東大街住宅地估值逾5億 業界：規模細具吸引力</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>新財政年度賣地表推出8幅中小型住宅地皮招標，當中有5幅改劃中的屬新增用地，規模最細為筲箕灣東大街地皮，可建總樓面約14.53萬方呎，最新市場估值約5.09至6.98億，每方呎樓面估值約3500至4800元。\n\n</p><h2>前身筲箕灣街市大廈 總樓面約14.53萬呎</h2>\n<p>上述筲箕灣東大街（筲箕灣內地段第860號）住宅地，現址為丟空7年的前筲箕灣街市大廈等用地，由「政府、機構或社區」地帶改劃為「住宅（甲類）7」地帶，主要是作高密度住宅發展，興建不高於110米的私人住宅。在建築物的最低三層，商業用途（例如商店及服務行業和食肆）屬經常准許的用途。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176721/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7586eaa72e5ee124a6a3a45b6cbe814a/2025-04/PR250228SKW07_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>項目地帶面積約1.6萬方呎，發展用地面積約1.56萬方呎，擬議地積比率限制方面，最高住用地積比率分為甲類地盤8倍、乙類地盤9倍和丙類地盤10倍，或最高非住用地積比率15倍。\n\n</p>\n<p>上述用地涉及可建總樓面約14.53萬方呎，綜合市場最新估值約5.09至6.98億，每方呎樓面估值約3500至4800元。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176722/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/05170a6e0d33d77c4e9473a313ee3fd0/2025-04/174374742381975.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>業界：港島區住宅地新供應罕有</h2>\n<p>泓亮諮詢及評估董事總經理張翹楚指出，地盤面積細，而且港島區地皮新供應一向罕有，亦位處市區地段，隨着新盤貨尾量日漸消化，認為規模細項目對發展商具吸引力。\n\n</p>\n<p>華坊諮詢評估資深董事梁沛泓表示，近年港島區住宅地新供應罕有，而且地盤規模不大，涉及投資額不多，而且項目位於筲箕灣東大街，四周民生配套設施齊全，料會受到市場歡迎。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062104/即時-地產-筲箕灣東大街住宅地估值逾5億-業界-規模細具吸引力",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-04 14:26:02",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "清明｜大批巿民祭祖掃墓 柴灣哥連臣角電梯上山要半個鐘 市民稱支持綠色殯葬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"柴灣哥連臣角人山人海。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/21bf1e068219ecd4e742c61eb3f2ffd6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040414145091900.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">柴灣哥連臣角人山人海。蘇正謙攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【清明節/掃墓/拜祭/拜山/哥連臣角】今日（4日）是清明節，不少孝子賢孫帶備香燭冥鏹等祭品，為先人掃墓及拜祭。上午大批市民帶備香燭冥鏹、鮮花、燒肉等祭品，到柴灣歌連臣角拜山。有市民表示，清明節為中國傳統節日，冀子女加深認識。有市民則指，支持當局推動「無煙拜祭」及綠色殯葬，稱最重要是一份心意。\n\n</p><h2>排隊搭電梯上山需時30分鐘</h2>\n<p>上午柴灣站人流眾多，附近屋邨多間食肆大排長龍。在連接柴灣新廈街與哥連臣角新廈靈灰安置所的扶手電梯入口處，警方在現場實施人流管制，排隊人龍逾100米，連同乘搭電梯的時間，記者花費近半小時上山。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176680/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"今日（4日）是清明節，不少孝子賢孫帶備香燭冥鏹等祭品前往掃墓。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/87d0142b8a916910f4be2418744cd34e/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125533972_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今日（4日）是清明節，不少孝子賢孫帶備香燭冥鏹等祭品前往掃墓。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176681/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"扶手電梯入口處，警方在現場實施人流管制，排隊人龍逾100米。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d808ee08cc21bc909fbe7929ce5ea63f/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125533972_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        扶手電梯入口處，警方在現場實施人流管制，排隊人龍逾100米。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176683/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"附近屋邨多間食肆滿座。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2336801f93058a7e4b0d39ebe52de4a8/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_132021611_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        附近屋邨多間食肆滿座。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176674/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"區先生表示，今日帶兩個就讀小學的女兒掃墓，讓她們認識中國傳統節日。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b305ac2930835b1aabec3c49d02f2c1e/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125718707_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        區先生表示，今日帶兩個就讀小學的女兒掃墓，讓她們認識中國傳統節日。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176673/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鍾太表示，每年都帶兒子一同祭祖。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa6d09f4ece5a79640d42eab35d42bcd/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125718707_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鍾太表示，每年都帶兒子一同祭祖。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176676/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"林先生表示，今年花費約500元購買香燭冥鏹。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/04fbb62a0f0f5aa6d8f8271fa44935ac/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125718707_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        林先生表示，今年花費約500元購買香燭冥鏹。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176675/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"余小姐認為當局推動「無煙拜祭」是好事。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eeb346ee1c3acd0e7c4205b0c81fe332/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125718707_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        余小姐認為當局推動「無煙拜祭」是好事。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176684/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市民清明節掃墓情況。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0af34a12b35e41c24b870259066682c1/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125533972_20.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市民清明節掃墓情況。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176685/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市民拜祭先人。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/080526c0c7bf703eff1c622a36147a5d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125533972_24.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市民拜祭先人。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176686/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市民到柴灣哥連臣角新廈靈灰安置所掃墓。蘇正謙攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c835074ee9676da80373f290cf684de/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_125552807_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市民到柴灣哥連臣角新廈靈灰安置所掃墓。蘇正謙攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>市民冀女兒認識中國傳統節日</h2>\n<p>區先生表示，今日帶兩個就讀小學的女兒掃墓，讓她們認識中國傳統節日，「清明節是要做這件事。小學常識科都會問到，起碼加深她們的認識」。他亦表示，會考慮身後將骨灰撒在紀念花園，「不用後輩那麼麻煩走上來，簡單一點」。\n\n</p><h2>市民支持當局推「無煙拜祭」</h2>\n<p>鍾太表示，每年都帶兒子一同祭祖，「讓他知道要尊敬祖先，讓祖先（保佑）大家開心心心，健健康康」。對於當局推動「無煙拜祭」，她認為會更環保，亦節省清理功夫，但指老一輩的習慣需時改變，「始終長者都喜歡有支香拜祭，有些火」。就讀小二的鍾小朋友笑言，今日帶燒肉、麵包等上山，冀大家「清明節快樂」。\n\n</p>\n<p>余小姐帶備鮮花、紙紮、燒肉等祭品掃墓，共花費約500至600元。她表示，扶手電梯便利市民上山，但由於有大批市民排隊，因此從山下排隊搭電梯上山也要花費約20分鐘。對於當局推動「無煙拜祭」及綠色殯葬，余小姐認為是好事，「可以省一些土地，還有最重要是心意」。\n\n</p>\n<p>林先生表示，今年花費約500元購買香燭冥鏹，而扶手電梯令上山過程輕鬆不少，「以前走很多石級，現在不用。以前行半小時，現在可能15分鐘」。他亦支持當局推動綠色殯葬，「我覺得是好事，一來環保，二來簡單一點，大家都不用那麼重負擔」。問及未來會否考慮綠色殯葬，林先生稱「都會的」。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者 蕭博禧\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062103/即時-港聞-清明-大批巿民祭祖掃墓-柴灣哥連臣角電梯上山要半個鐘-市民稱支持綠色殯葬",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-04 14:26:02",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "沈陽大樓大火 兩名消防員殉職",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/60ad9bec111b71f0bff55014c1da0102/5cf48e33930a48eeb9656826de2e8abc-8313156b309dd63b4302a4d22fe27aee-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ef794c482b0\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ef794c482b1\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/381687854b21c6ecc58080ae2a998068/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040414062238436.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>瀋陽一幢綜合性大樓，星期三（4月2日）發生火災，兩名消防員被困火場，救出後搶救無效殉職。\n\n</p>\n<p>瀋陽市消防支隊星期五（4日）在微博通報，火災發生在4月2日傍晚5時許，地點為瀋陽市鐵西區。接到報警後，瀋陽市消防救援支隊立即調派力量前往處置，安全營救出41名被困群眾。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"沈陽一棟綜合大樓發生火警。　微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/71c310e7bebb804b62a04c6b7b871bc8/2025-04/0404016.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        沈陽一棟綜合大樓發生火警。　微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"沈陽一棟綜合大樓發生火警。　微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/baf0047a09f4db5bbd280966df4a84ca/2025-04/0404017.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        沈陽一棟綜合大樓發生火警。　微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"消防員在現場救援。　微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b61a996aae88b219fc0c02c2bd88a887/2025-04/0404018.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防員在現場救援。　微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"綜火樓大火，現場農濃煙。　微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f0a509a9d3c04156bc51c54ddb0bcb8/2025-04/0404019.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        綜火樓大火，現場農濃煙。　微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"綜火樓大火，現場農濃煙。　微博\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a3f6dbfba66f262c9d78b9790d0012f0/2025-04/0404021.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        綜火樓大火，現場農濃煙。　微博\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>「在內攻搜救人員時，騰飛二街消防救援站站長王勛、班長宋思玉遇火情突變，被困火場，救出後立即送醫救治，因搶救無效壯烈犧牲。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
