            "title": "清明節新界多處火龍亂舞　元朗雞公嶺  馬鞍山村火勢猛烈",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"大批消防到錦田太陽谷救火。fb：錦田鄉\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b451f7bf0605c02b79af118eed33e1fb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040413475899374.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">大批消防到錦田太陽谷救火。fb：錦田鄉</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今天清明節，新界多處出現山火，今年1月11日發生山火的元朗雞公嶺再現火龍，山坡大片面積焚毀，濃煙席捲半空，附近錦田太陽谷附近亦有山火，消防員到場撲救。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176665/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大批消防到錦田太陽谷救火。fb：錦田鄉\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8981056e170e832453aebe60c687cf95/2025-04/488462835_122236783328207815_5615179691713586425_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大批消防到錦田太陽谷救火。fb：錦田鄉\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176666/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"錦田太陽谷附近現火龍。fb：錦田鄉\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e256b997eca692f9456bd7740657113/2025-04/488494111_122236783364207815_4188945150275251341_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        錦田太陽谷附近現火龍。fb：錦田鄉\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176667/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"元朗雞公嶺再現火龍。fb：錦田鄉\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/90a3073e51be5dd175947ad194744e16/2025-04/488887512_983427027248601_6510723879805766320_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        元朗雞公嶺再現火龍。fb：錦田鄉\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176654/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e0314dd05487f791d948b93c2c40bf2/2025-04/05.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176655/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1b4efaa2c71b001de7f60ea4e9b6fc87/2025-04/06.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176656/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/28a33f44edd3e2fcd731308ac79ff2ba/2025-04/07.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4176657/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/53bd25dd56600b2359fd70a8e139a6c9/2025-04/08.PNG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬鞍山村亦發生山火。fb：岳人 Geo Trekker  \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>中午12時許，粉嶺沙頭角路馬尾下段、近河壩村對開山坡發生山火，火勢鄰近居民。消防人員趕抵現場，山坡一墳頭冒煙，至下午1時撲熄，無人受傷。與此同時，馬鞍山村對開山頭亦告失守，火勢猛烈，大批消防上山撲救。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
